^Help - AFK
USAGE: .afk ^message
WHERE: ^message^ is an optional message to display.

Use this command when you want to tell people you have gone ^A^way ^F^rom
your ^K^eyboard.

EXAMPLES
  .afk
  .afk has left the room for a minute, be right back!

To get back from afk, just start typing again.

SEE ALSO
